---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Ondo Summit 2025 — AES" bodyClass="inner-page">

  <div class="container-fluid event-hero">
    <div class="event-hero-inner">
      <div class="event-hero-left">
        <div class="event-location">New York City, USA</div>
        <div class="event-title">Ondo<br />Summit<br />2025</div>
        <div class="event-tagline">
          Wall Street 2.0 launch event for 250 invite-only institutional investors and crypto visionaries at The Appel Room at Lincoln Center
        </div>
        <div class="event-hero-photo">
          <div class="event-hero-photo-item" style="background-image: url('/images/work1.png')"></div>
          <div class="event-hero-photo-item" style="background-image: url('/images/work2.png')"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-hero-right">
        <div class="event-detail-card">
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Production</div>
            <p>We had 3 months to plan the inaugural Ondo Summit, working with the small but incredible team at Ondo. We selected the Appel Room at Jazz at Lincoln Center, which had a mandatory production team and is a union venue, something we generally try to avoid. In this case, we had a wonderful experience with production partners who were as invested as we were in delivering a product at our level.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Staging</div>
            <p>We worked closely with Ondo's in-house designer and our colleagues at Europalco in Lisbon to collaborate on the stage design. The beautiful Appel Room has particular quirks that we had to work around, but we planned for enough setup time to account for any last minute changes or issues.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">On-Site Highlights</div>
            <p>A last minute snow storm worried us the night before - but we were pleasantly surprised to have a full house and gorgeous backdrop to kick off the 2025 crypto calendar with vibrant energy and a buzzworthy agenda.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-gallery">
    <div class="event-gallery-inner">
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <div class="gallery-placeholder gallery-large" style="background-image: url('/images/work3.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work5.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work7.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder gallery-large" style="background-image: url('/images/work9.png')"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-back">
    <div class="event-back-inner">
      <a href="/work" class="cr-btn white ex-padding">← Back to All Events</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
